# K 180 Q 3.5: filter above fundamental, resonance adds sub bloom
# NO high Q — the reference doesn't show resonant ringing
v0 w0 a2 t 0.022 0.180 0 0 f 49 q0 F1,30,49 J1 K 180 Q 3.5 H1,-1,-1,-1 l1
